1. *Ubijanje* životinja je krivično delo. (Killing animals is a criminal offense.)
2. Oni su *ubijali* vreme igrajući video igre. (They were killing time playing video games.)
3. Pripadnici vojske su bili zaduženi za *ubijanje* neprijatelja. (Soldiers were tasked with killing the enemy.)
4. Njegova želja za *ubijanjem* svojih neprijatelja je postala opsesivna. (His desire to kill his enemies became obsessive.)
5. *Ubijanje* dosade postalo je moj hobi. (Killing boredom has become my hobby.)
6. Usporavanje saobraćaja *ubija* produktivnost grada. (Slowing down traffic kills the productivity of the city.)
7. Oni su *ubijeni* u saobraćajnoj nesreći. (They were killed in a car accident.)
8. Policija je brzo reagovala i *ubila* napadača. (The police quickly responded and killed the attacker.)
9. Film je uključivao mnogo scena nasilja i *ubijanja*. (The movie included a lot of scenes of violence and killing.)
10. Ubistvo je najozbiljniji oblik *ubijanja*. (Murder is the most serious form of killing.)